cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.DS, cs.SI 

This paper proposes a framework for constructing ensemble learning methods from kernel methods, which is a topic related to machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses the design of new multi-class ensemble learning methods, which is related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and computer vision (cs.CV). Additionally, the paper presents experimental results, which suggests that it may also belong to the data structures (cs.DS) and social and information networks (cs.SI) sub-categories.
